This bottle was the wine from cellar roulette tonight. 
The nose is room filling. A little mineralness, melded red fruit - just a stand out before you even raise the glass. 
There are wines that just announce themselves,&hellip;

If you hate ‘em please just close the post and move on. 
Six wines served and no real landmines encountered.  Agua de Mar was the setting, our favorite Centro restaurant. 

Orange Pinot Grigio from NE Italy.  Perfumed &hellip;
